PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Communications of CLAUDETTE ROY, of Edmonton, Alberta, GLORIA WEBSTER, of Alert Bay, British Columbia, PIERRE DUFOUR, Aylmer, Quebec, RICHARD ALWAY, of Toronto, Ontario, and ROBERT BOTHWELL, of Toronto, Ontario, as trustees of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Civilization, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
